QuestData.Title: Lay of the Land
QuestData.Description: Curse these furry pests! Kill one, and two more rise in its place...$b$bNothing has changed, $n. Orders are orders, no matter how few of us stand and regardless of the odds.$b$bI have plans to make and problems to solve.$b$bI want you to get out there and learn the lay of the land. Don't return until you have something useful to report.$b$bAnd silence that yammering fool while you're out there!$b$bDismissed!
QuestData.LogDescription: Visit the Shrine of the Sun, the Shrine of the Moon, and Kill Dook Ookem.
